column5: I sure wish it was I,but sadly not. Had a fella ask for some ties. Sent off this morning. All but the bead head, are on the way. Some weighted some not.
Build it and they will come, seems to be working for you.
Good looking bunch of flies Brian.  	You'll forgive me if my mind went immediately here at the thread title.   😁
Great one, I hadn't heard that in ages.
